snippet.textDisplay:
Aay Rahe Haq k Shaheedon. Its means that people that stood for the right path.
I don't if the rest of the world is able to understand the feelings we Pakistani get after listening to this national song. We have lost more than 10,000 Army men and more than 60,000 civilians at the hands of terrorism. We are in a state of War. The rest of the world needs to understand that Pakistan and its people are continuesly fighting with this disease and This song is a tribute to the Pakistanis that have sacrificed their todays for our tomorrows.
Tmhe is watan ki Hawaiian Salam kehti hain❤
